Contents of files
-----------------

sapfl.tgz -> CAPE v0.1
	first version of CAPE based on complete checkpoints
	only loops and sections are translated
	SAPFL = Semi Automatic Parallelization of For Loops

dompcc.tgz -> CAPE v0.1.1
	first version of CAPE using TXL instead of Lex and Yacc
	DOMPCC = Distributed OpenMP C Compiler

dompcc_Comment.tar.gz -> CAPE V0.1.2
	extended version of the previous one

20171001 TXL Transform.tgz -> v0.1.3
	amélioration de la traduction avec TXL

cape50.tgz -> CAPE v0.2
	second version of CAPE based on DICKPT (home made incremental checkpoint)
	CAPE = Checkpointing Aided Parallel Execution
	DICKPT = Discontinuous Checkpointer

201811280045cape700.tgz -> CAPE v0.3
	third version of CAPE that includes more OpenMP constructs
